law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 348, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1996. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 87, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1994.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Medical professional liability insurance for charitable health care facilities and volunteer caregivers -- Fee on physicians and attorneys for payment of premiums.
